### Enviar mensagem
POST http://localhost:3000/whatsapp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "to": "5585998546812",
    "message": "Alef Oliveira testando o envio de mensagem"
}

### Verificar webhook
GET http://localhost:3000/whatsapp/webhook?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=tokenAlef12345&hub.challenge=123456


### Simular webhook (mensagem recebida)
POST http://localhost:3000/whatsapp/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "object": "whatsapp_business_account",
    "entry": [{
        "id": "123456789",
        "changes": [{
            "value": {
                "messaging_product": "whatsapp",
                "metadata": {
                    "display_phone_number": "5585998546812",
                    "phone_number_id": "123456789"
                },
                "messages": [{
                    "from": "5585998546812",
                    "id": "wamid.123456789",
                    "timestamp": "1234567890",
                    "text": {
                        "body": "Teste de mensagem"
                    },
                    "type": "text"
                }]
            }
        }]
    }]
}

